videos.description: Matt McQuaid fools the defense with a crafty no-look pass to Xavier Tillman, who rises up for the strong two-handed jam.
videos.headline: McQuaid's no-look pass sets up Tillman's slam

videos.description: Andre Wesson backs down Cassius Winston and finds Musa Jallow, who puts away a one-handed slam to trim MSU's lead.
videos.headline: OSU's Wesson feeds Jallow for big finish

videos.description: Matt McQuaid crosses up C.J. Jackson, then gets Andre Wesson with a nasty ball-fake before finishing with a finger roll at the rim.
videos.headline: McQuaid schools defense for smooth finish
